OL,2,M🔒Lock Picking Robot! 🤖🔓
OL,4,CEtienne Naude
OL,5,CSun 16:50-17:10
OL,6,CStage B
OL,8,GAn open source lock-picking robot,
OL,9,Gwhich counterintuitively is designed
OL,10,Gto make locks more secure. Made as an
OL,11,Galternative to master keys, which are
OL,12,Gused widely (for example, on almost
OL,13,Gevery suitcase) and have large
OL,14,Ginherent security issues. The
OL,15,Glockpicking robot uses a series of
OL,16,Gwires which push through a custom
OL,17,G3D-printed steel key blank to spoof
OL,18,Gthe correct key bitting.
OL,19,Ggithub.com/etinaude/unlocked 🔒➡️🔑🤖➡️🔓
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
